      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am absolutely thrilled to be listing my pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and looks absolutely flawless inside and out. It drives like a total dream and still has that 'new car' magic. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make someone very, very happy! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
