    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe in Carbon Black Metallic. This example is powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been fully overhauled with Beisan components for peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis is superlative; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with TMS plates to ensure structural rigidity under high cornering loads. Maintenance is current, including a recent valve adjustment and preventative rod bearing replacement with ARP hardware. The factory-spec limited-slip differential and 6-speed manual transmission operate with mechanical perfection. All suspension bushings have been refreshed to maintain the original kinematic precision of the E46 chassis. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver's car for the technical purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
