    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade example, meticulously preserved in showroom condition. The exterior boasts a mirror-like finish with a professional-grade ceramic coating, free of stone chips, swirls, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolster wear, the carpets are pristine under original floor mats, and it has never been smoked in. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is flawless, supported by a comprehensive binder of service records. It has been strictly garage-kept, never driven in rain or snow, and recently underwent a full fluid service and multi-point inspection. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key, investment-quality vehicle.",
